<div id="instagram-marketing-tools"></div>
<h2>Free Instagram marketing tools</h2>
<p>Need help with your Instagram marketing? That‚Äôs okay‚Äîyou&#8217;re not alone! Most businesses do use some form of Instagram marketing assistance as it can be a huge undertaking. Luckily, there are a ton of free and low-cost Instagram marketing tools out there for you to take advantage of, like these ones below.</p>
<h3>Meta Instagram Creator hub</h3>
<p>Meta has its own <a href="https://creators.instagram.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram marketing hub</a> for businesses and creators looking to get started on the platform.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/instagram-marketing-creator-hub.webp" alt="instagram marketing - creator hub from meta" width="900" height="363" class="aligncenter wp-image-94275 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/instagram-marketing-creator-hub.webp 900w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/instagram-marketing-creator-hub-480x194.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 900px, 100vw" /></p>
